  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Due to [`.gitattributes`](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/.gitattributes) which forces autocrlf for text files (`* text=auto`), the checkout on Windows is done with CRLF line endings, which breaks Docker builds:\r\n\r\n```\r\nStep 4/9 : RUN cd /go-ethereum && make geth\r\n ---> Running in 30c5201981ca\r\nbuild/env.sh go run build/ci.go install ./cmd/geth\r\nmake: build/env.sh: Command not found\r\nmake: *** [Makefile:15: geth] Error 127\r\nThe command '/bin/sh -c cd /go-ethereum && make geth' returned a non-zero code: 2\r\n```\r\n\r\nSuggesting to remove `.gitattributes`, since there is no workaround (no override possibility for `.gitattributes`).",
