    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "`* text=auto` is very dangerous, it mangles files, you should not use it. Better to specify exactly what extensions are text, and what mode they should use, e.g. `.sh text=lf`, `.bat text=crlf`. We dropped ethereum support, so I don't need this anymore, but please make a note of it.",
